# 🗺️ B-Vista Roadmap

Welcome to the official roadmap for **B-Vista**!

This document outlines our **short-term**, **mid-term**, and **long-term** goals as we build out the platform.

---

## ✅ Recently Completed

- [x] Initial public release (v1.1.1)
- [x] Live WebSocket-powered UI with React + AG Grid
- [x] Built-in datasets + API data connectors
- [x] Interactive session management
- [x] UI for missing data, transformation, editing, and summary stats

---

## 🔜 Short-Term (v1.2.x - v1.3.x)

- [ ] Dark mode toggle
- [ ] Data export (CSV, Excel, PNG) from UI
- [ ] Column filter presets + saved views
- [ ] Improved session recovery
- [ ] Add keyboard shortcuts
- [ ] UI tooltips & onboarding hints
- [ ] First community contribution merged ✅

---

## 🚧 Mid-Term Goals

- [ ] Plugin system for custom EDA modules
- [ ] User-authenticated multi-user mode


---

## 🌐 Long-Term Vision

- [ ] Full multi-user collaboration (real-time editing)
- [ ] B-Vista Cloud for hosted EDA + sharing
- [ ] Integration with major ML platforms (Hugging Face, Weights & Biases, etc.)
- [ ] Native support for Polars and Arrow DataFrames

---

## 🙋‍♀️ Want to Help?

- Check out [good first issues](https://github.com/Baci-Ak/b-vista/issues?q=is%3Aissue+is%3Aopen+label%3A%22good+first+issue%22)
- Join our [Discussions](https://github.com/Baci-Ak/b-vista/discussions)
- Submit PRs or ideas — we review them all!

---

📌 *This roadmap is a living document — expect updates regularly as the project evolves.*
